Package org.forgerock.openig.log

Facility for logging and real-time performance monitoring.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
LogSink Receives and handles log entries.
 

Class Summary
ConsoleLogSink A sink that writes log entries to the standard error stream.
ConsoleLogSink.Heaplet Creates and initializes a console sink in a heap environment.
FileLogSink A sink that writes log entries to a file.
FileLogSink.Heaplet Creates and initializes a console sink in a heap environment.
LogEntry The log entry data structure.
Logger Wraps a log sink and exposes a set of convenience methods for various logging activities.
LogMetric Log entry data that provides a measurement.
LogTimer Records elapsed time in a log in milliseconds.
NullLogSink A sink that discards all log entries.
 

Enum Summary
LogLevel Levels used for categorizing log entries.
